<html><body>
<div id="content-container" style="width:640px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
  <div id="content-body" style="padding: 20px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #dddddd; border-radius: 3px; line-height: 2em; font-family: Arial">
    <p>Hi {{fullname}},</p>
    <p>We received a request to verify your email as {{email}}. If this is correct, please click the button below.</p>
    <p><a style="color: #ffffff; background-color: #1e990e; padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem 0.9375rem 1.75rem; font-size: 0.8125rem; text-decoration: none" href="{{verify_email_url}}"><strong>Verify Email</strong></a></p>
    <p><b>Why did I get this email?</b><br>We received a request to verify the email address for your account ({{username}}).</p>
    <p>If you did not request this, you can just delete this email.</p>
  </div>
  {% include "emails/footer.html" %}
</div>
</body></html>
